title: Izzat
subTitle: Constable Ram Chandra teaches his son Siddharth to be a diligent policeman and lead his life with honesty and dignity. Siddharth follows his advice until circumstances force him to leave his ideals.

title: Akbar Birbal

title: Dost
subTitle: A forest ranger joins hands with locals to prevent large-scale poaching that is prevalent in the nearby forests. However, his efforts infuriate a poaching baron who vows to exact revenge.

title: Kundan
subTitle: Thakur Shamsher Singh, a wealthy criminal, tries to befriend a newly-appointed police officer in order to gain his favour, only to find out that the policeman is immune to his tactics.

title: Mera Gaon Mera Desh
subTitle: When Ajit, a former prisoner, learns of Jabbar who is terrorising the people of his village, he decides to stand up against him. However, things take a turn when Jabbar abducts Ajit's lover.

title: Kohram
subTitle: Colonel Balbir Singh Sodhi assumes a disguise to unveil the true colours of Veer Bhadra Singh, a corrupt minister. Soon, Major Ajit teams up with him to execute the mission.

title: Rajput
subTitle: Janaki, a young woman, loves Manu Pratap Singh but is forced to marry Dhirendra, a police inspector. However, when she gets kidnapped by a man, who tries to rape her, Manu saves her in time.

title: Kurukshetra
subTitle: ACP Prithviraj, an honest man, arrests Chief Minister Baburao's son for raping a woman. Consequently, Baburao leaves no stone unturned to get revenge against Prithviraj.

title: Haan Maine Bhi Pyaar Kiya
subTitle: Pooja divorces her husband for being unfaithful and gets a job as secretary to a film star. The two fall in love, before her ex-husband returns and she finds herself confused between the two men.

title: Phool Aur Angaar
subTitle: A young man rescues a woman from being molested but gets accused of the heinous crime instead. Trying to apprehend the miscreants, he gets caught in a web of deception and lies.

title: Janta Ki Adalat
subTitle: DSP Jyoti foils the plans of Shankar, a prisoner who threatens to kill a minister. But she lends her support to Shankar after she hears about the minister's dark secrets and ill intentions.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Aakhree Raasta

title: Jis Desh Mein Ganga Rehta Hai
subTitle: Ganga, an innocent man, is raised by a foster couple in a village. When he is brought back to his family in the city, he struggles to fit into modern society.

title: Gambler
subTitle: Though Inspector Dayashanker is lazy, he unwittingly unearths a criminal conspiracy and becomes the pride of his division overnight. However, a local gangsters turn his life into a nightmare.
